Description: hatena-haiker: Python 3 Wrapper for Hatena Haiku API
        ====================================================
        
        hatena-haiker is a simple library handling `Hatena Haiku <http://h.hatena.ne.jp/>`_ API.
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            >>> import haiker
            >>> auth = haiker.OAuth(
            ...    'MyConsumerKey', 'MyConsumerSecret',
            ...     'MyAccessToken', 'MyAccessTokenSecret'
            ... )
            >>> api = haiker.Haiku(auth)
            >>> api.public_timeline(count=3)
            [{'created_at': '...',
              'favorited': '...',
              'id': '...',
              'in_reply_to_status_id': '',
              'in_reply_to_user_id': '',
              'keyword': '...',
              'link': '...',
              'replies': [...],
              'source': '...',
              'target': {...},
              'text': '....',
              'user': {'followers_count': '...',
                       'id': '...',
                       'name': '...',
                       'profile_image_url': '...',
                       'screen_name': '...',
                       'url': 'http://h.hatena.ne.jp/...'}},
             {...},
             {...}]
        
        
